snippet.title: Lil Wayne Faces 10 Yrs In Prison
snippet.description:
Lil Wayne Faces 10 Yrs In Prison
Subscribe Here ☛ http://bit.ly/2xB5CqA
Recent Uploads: https://bit.ly/3qF38D7


Recently rapper Lil Wayne was arrested and charged by federal prosecutors in Miami with illegal possession of a gun as a convicted felon. This complaint alleged that Dwayne Michael Carter Jr, was in possession of a firearm on December 23rd, 2019, as reported by ABC News. However today this case has finally come to a close with a guilty plea coming from Lil Wayne. I'm going to break it all down for you right here on iO.
